鬥，甚至有所付出及犧牲。<br />\n<br />\n12月10日晚，我們一起站出來，為香港人加油，也為全球為人權奮鬥的人打氣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">日期：12月10日<br />\n時間：18:30-22:00<br />\n地點：金鐘連儂牆下<br />\n</span><br />\n內容：<br />\n悼念及回顧<br />\n嘉賓講話<br />\n短片欣賞及分享<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LCPK0vx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLCPK0vx.jpg&h=63585984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n推呀屌你再過4個鐘就係啦 唔好再屌鬼啦行動post呢文宣post呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係完咗人權日遊行就end game㗎<br />\n我地仲有訴求㗎！！！<br />\n聽日要見到連儂牆有十萬人呀！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n12月10號 6點半政總見！！"},{"pid":"115fb7158b2f51f9247a9841fa7ba0e38b161188","tid":1777302,"uid":213163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a9188f9a59c122444d370458f2a79494bddc324","tid":1777302,"uid":308199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T06:21:07.000Z","msg":"本老母為深黃，好支持示威者，出街食黃店，日日接收黃色資訊，但就衰在成日捉鬼，放火燒法院係鬼，早兩日軍火庫又係鬼，割頸火燒人通通係鬼。口識講兄弟爬山，但思想上完全跟唔到。可以點搞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T06:40:55.000Z","msg":"教到伯母嘅話 成個連登就有救 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e0e07311232f8fccf78d06a86526ee88ad12b0","tid":1777302,"uid":292987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T06:44:12.000Z","msg":"問佢係咪認為黑警唔抵劏 法院唔抵燒 和平示威可以解決到所有問題 令政府跪低<br />\n如果佢話係嘅咁我都冇嘢好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2788128996a610e92ce89cf12514fc9b3e1dcd8a","tid":1777302,"uid":308199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"614f042887562c9082b100f79c372a889f45fdd6","tid":1777302,"uid":184370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T06:28:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T06:56:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a